motor_yaml:
# Single fed Tubular motors use Z-R (axial-radial) coordinate system.
# All dimensions in millimeters (mm), currents in Amperes (A).

output:
  folder_path: models/iron_tubular
  file_name: motor
  
model:
  number_slots: 6           # Number of coils within armature
  number_poles: 2           # Number of poles under the armature at any instant
  extra_pairs: 5            # Extra pairs (N-S) to approximate infinite track 
  d_currents: 0             # Direct-axis current (A)
  q_currents: 4             # Quadrature-axis current (A)
  fill_factor: 0.70         # Fraction of the slot filled by the slot material 
  boundary_material: Air

slot:
  inner_radius: 7.25        # Inner radius of the slot
  outer_radius: 15          # Outer radius of the slot 
  axial_length: 6.30        # Length along axial (Z) direction
  axial_spacing: 1.2        # Spacing between slots along axial direction
  material: 0.4mm           # FEMM Material for the wire (Check FEMM Material Library)
  wire_diameter: 0.4        # Diameter of the wire 

yoke:
  inner_radius: 15          # Inner radius of the yoke
  outer_radius: 17.75       # Outer radius of the yoke
  material: "Pure Iron"     # FEMM Material for the yoke (Check FEMM Material Library)

pole:
  inner_radius: 2.5         # Inner radius of the pole 
  outer_radius: 6           # Outer radius of the pole 
  axial_length: 15          # Length of the pole along axial direction 
  material: N52             # Magnet grade  (Check FEMM Material Library)
